    		<h1><a href="/">Fancybox - simple and fancy jquery plugin</a></h1>
    		<div><a href="/fancybox/fancybox_1.0.0.zip"><img id="download" src="/img/down.png" alt="Download" style="width:162px;height:46px;" /></a></div>
